---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Portfolio">
<main class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<!-- Hero Header Section -->
<header class="mb-20">
<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-secondary-container/30 border border-outline-variant/15 rounded-full text-primary-fixed-dim text-xs font-label tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">
<span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed-dim animate-pulse"></span>
Case Studies
</div>
<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl xl:text-8xl font-bold leading-[0.9] tracking-tighter font-headline md: font-bold mb-6 max-w-4xl text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
                ENGINEERING THE <span class="text-primary-fixed-dim">FUTURE</span> OF VECTOR LOGIC.
            </h1>
<p class="font-body text-on-surface-variant text-lg max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
                Explore how Kinetic Intelligence transforms complex enterprise challenges into streamlined, AI-driven architectures. Precise, efficient, and relentlessly innovative.
            </p>
</header>
<!-- Projects Bento Grid -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-6">
<!-- Case Study 1: Large Featured Card -->
<section class="lg:col-span-12 group relative bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-outline-variant/15 transition-all duration-500 hover:bg-surface-container">
<div class="node-indicator"></div>
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 h-full">
<div class="p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col justify-between">
<div>
<div class="flex gap-2 mb-6">
<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-secondary-container/30 text-on-secondary-container text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase rounded">Automation</span>
<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-container/20 text-primary-fixed-dim text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase rounded">AI Engine</span>
</div>
<h2 class="font-headline text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-primary">AI Customer Service Automation</h2>
<div class="space-y-6">
<div>
<h3 class="font-label text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-outline mb-2">Project Overview</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Deployed a neural-linguistic processing layer for a Fortune 500 logistics firm to handle 85% of tier-1 support queries without human intervention.</p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
<div>
<h3 class="font-label text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-outline mb-2">The Problem</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs">Latency in response times leading to 22% customer churn during peak hours.</p>
</div>
<div>
<h3 class="font-label text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-outline mb-2">The Solution</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs">Vector-based intent mapping and real-time sentiment analysis engine.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-outline-variant/10 flex items-center justify-between">
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
<span class="font-label text-[10px] text-primary-fixed-dim">PYTHON</span>
<span class="font-label text-[10px] text-primary-fixed-dim">PYTORCH</span>
<span class="font-label text-[10px] text-primary-fixed-dim">AWS SAGE</span>
</div>
<div class="text-right">
<span class="block font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">92%</span>
<span class="block font-label text-[10px] text-outline uppercase tracking-tighter">Efficiency Gain</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="relative min-h-[300px] bg-surface-container-highest">
<img alt="AI neural network visualization" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover mix-blend-screen opacity-60" data-alt="abstract 3d visualization of glowing blue neural network nodes and data connections in a dark void atmosphere" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDmLFYLahTEmMSK1yVFE_FqRIT3NtXlpIndCYmBLhDVUI-dHeyCoaqo1gADQIERMptDFI0lsr_Fd1rqqVY2-yTCbn-JT423qP5wsdhjY6efrghXeIyg80412U9ahadA4Ga1fWYbkyn2sj-HcPBQGFeomAOYIDAS9-JcG0dYT0VnXACjdHQuLLjwkEjRTwG-ySyDiz9wV5vj7FfuecisMF-2R-Jc6P6vNIo38JUZVYANVKCtLGxDo4L5otgCkelT42c4rN6H7ilB8iGp"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-l from-transparent via-transparent to-surface-container-low md:block hidden"></div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Case Study 2: System Integration Platform -->
<section class="lg:col-span-7 group relative bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-outline-variant/15 transition-all duration-500">
<div class="p-8">
<div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-12">
<div>
<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-secondary-container/30 text-on-secondary-container text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase rounded">Infrastructure</span>
<h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold mt-4 text-primary">System Integration Platform</h2>
</div>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed-dim text-3xl">hub</span>
</div>
<div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
<div>
<h3 class="font-label text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-outline mb-2">The Problem</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm italic">"Siloed legacy data prevented real-time decision making across global offices."</p>
</div>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            We architected a unified API mesh that bridged 14 disparate ERP systems into a single source of truth, enabling millisecond data propagation.
                        </p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 py-6 border-y border-outline-variant/10">
<div>
<h3 class="font-label text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-outline mb-1">Technology</h3>
<div class="text-xs text-on-surface font-medium">GraphQL, Kubernetes, Kafka</div>
</div>
<div>
<h3 class="font-label text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-outline mb-1">Result</h3>
<div class="text-xs text-primary-fixed-dim font-bold">400ms Average Latency</div>
</div>
</div>
<button class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-primary-fixed-dim group-hover:gap-4 transition-all">
                        Deep Dive Technicals <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
</button>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Case Study 3: Digital Business Dashboard -->
<section class="lg:col-span-5 group relative bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-outline-variant/15 transition-all duration-500">
<div class="h-48 relative overflow-hidden bg-surface-container-high">
<img alt="Digital dashboard visualization" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-40 group-hover:grayscale-0 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-700" data-alt="futuristic digital dashboard with glowing cyan data charts and abstract architectural geometric lines on a dark interface" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBvTKlNzDKiDxig-9NlnFGm4VJfQIuBzi_rIRcJIZ3LKqj_13_kxvkl-cIHn0BET7CSLGHPq1NLcU3JZcCk9w05iSVjT_O5UPRdncDxf0pjS-RMutGJh6Uf6lh8761kp2FCx1oHh0KxqBI33ftKAbenXpAGohWWl3UDf-gbX5xJQxrcLs7G2d_gjPDVzFL8ZdyWuBtlIQT3eoWvTDfI5C5YwAiZoOAsWxEo-TRhisoAYoGt-XRo-gCrrhcMYkh_zJZ6FUKxoO7kp6zV"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-surface-container-low to-transparent"></div>
</div>
<div class="p-8 -mt-10 relative z-10">
<h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-primary">Digital Business Dashboard</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                        A high-fidelity visualization suite for executive-level oversight, featuring predictive modeling and risk assessment simulations.
                    </p>
<div class="space-y-4">
<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
<span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary-fixed-dim rounded-full"></span>
<span class="text-xs text-on-surface">Predictive Market Simulation</span>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
<span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary-fixed-dim rounded-full"></span>
<span class="text-xs text-on-surface">Real-time Risk Indexing</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-outline-variant/10 flex justify-between items-end">
<div>
<span class="font-label text-[10px] text-outline block uppercase mb-1">Visual Stack</span>
<span class="text-xs font-bold">React + D3.js</span>
</div>
<div class="p-3 bg-surface-container-high rounded-lg text-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">monitoring</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</div>
<!-- Metric Section (Horizontal Banner) -->
<div class="mt-24 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 py-12 border-y border-outline-variant/10">
<div class="text-center md:text-left">
<span class="block font-headline text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">50+</span>
<span class="block font-label text-[10px] tracking-widest text-outline uppercase">Global Deployments</span>
</div>
<div class="text-center md:text-left">
<span class="block font-headline text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">99.9%</span>
<span class="block font-label text-[10px] tracking-widest text-outline uppercase">Uptime Performance</span>
</div>
<div class="text-center md:text-left">
<span class="block font-headline text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">$1.2B</span>
<span class="block font-label text-[10px] tracking-widest text-outline uppercase">Optimized Capital</span>
</div>
<div class="text-center md:text-left">
<span class="block font-headline text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">12ms</span>
<span class="block font-label text-[10px] tracking-widest text-outline uppercase">System Latency</span>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Contact CTA -->
<section class="mt-24 kinetic-gradient p-1 overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
<div class="bg-surface-dim rounded-[calc(0.75rem-3px)] p-12 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-24 bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl -mr-12 -mt-12"></div>
<h2 class="font-headline text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 relative z-10 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">READY TO INTEGRATE YOUR FUTURE?</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10 relative z-10">Our engineers are standing by to audit your existing architecture and propose a kinetic roadmap for intelligence-driven growth.</p>
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center relative z-10">
<button class="kinetic-gradient text-on-primary-fixed px-10 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold w-full md:w-auto font-headline shadow-lg shadow-primary-fixed-dim/40 dark:shadow-primary-fixed-dim/20 hover:brightness-110 transition-all">Consult with an Architect</button>
<button class="px-10 py-4 border border-outline-variant/30 hover:border-primary-fixed-dim transition-all text-sm font-bold tracking-widest uppercase w-full md:w-auto text-slate-900 dark:text-white">View Technical Docs</button>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>

<style>
.glass-panel {
    background: rgba(16, 20, 26, 0.6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
}
.kinetic-gradient {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4cd6ff 0%, #006178 100%);
}
.node-indicator {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 4px;
    height: 4px;
    background-color: #d2f2ff;
}
</style>
</BaseLayout>
